summary: This FBI document details the arrest of Alfredo Rodriguez on December 8, 2009, pursuant to a federal warrant for Obstruction of Justice. It notes the arrest was made without incident in West Palm Beach, Florida, and Rodriguez was transported to the Palm Beach County Jail.
